      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah i get the dice thing. but it still feels like there's something actually \"hidden\" or \"mysterious\" going on under the surface that we just can't see. is there any way to describe that \"hidden\" part without just saying it's magic or random? like, what is actually happening in that gap between maybe seeing one particle and the other one reacting?",
